  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Treasury Direction made by the Chancellor under Sections 71 and 76 of the Coronavirus Act 2020
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The Chancellor has made a further Treasury Direction in relation to Grant 3 under Sections 71 and 76 of the Coronavirus Act 2020.</p>

  </div>
</div>

